===Etymology===
From {{etyl|goh|de}} {{term|frī|lang=goh}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|de}} {{m|gem-pro|*frijaz}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|de}} {{m|ine-pro|*prei-||to be fond of}}, {{m|ine-pro|*prey-}}. Compare Dutch {{term|vrij|lang=nl}}, English {{term|free|lang=en}}, Danish {{term|fri|lang=da}}.

===Pronunciation===
